import {
  Accordion,
  AccordionDetails,
  AccordionSummary,
  Grid,
  Typography,
} from "@material-ui/core";
import {
  AccountCircle,
  ExpandMore,
  HomeRounded,
  PhoneAndroidRounded,
} from "@material-ui/icons";
import FormSpacer from "components/FormSpacer";
import React from "react";
import InputCustomize from "./components/InputCustomize";
import SwitchCustomize from "./components/SwitchCustomize";
import { structure } from "./structure";

function ProfileForm(props) {
  const [checked, setChecked] = React.useState(false);
  return (
    <form>
      {structure.map((item, index) => {
        return (
          <Accordion>
            <AccordionSummary
              expandIcon={<ExpandMore />}
              aria-controls="panel1a-content"
              id="panel1a-header"
            >
              <Typography>{item.section}</Typography>
            </AccordionSummary>
          </Accordion>
        );
      })}
      {/* <Accordion>
        <AccordionSummary
          expandIcon={<ExpandMore />}
          aria-controls="panel1a-content"
          id="panel1a-header"
        >
          <Typography>Infomation</Typography>
        </AccordionSummary>
        <AccordionDetails>
          <Grid container spacing={3}>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="First Name"
                icon={() => <AccountCircle color="primary" />}
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Last Name"
                icon={() => <AccountCircle color="primary" />}
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={2}>
              <SwitchCustomize
                checked={checked}
                handleChange={(e) => setChecked(e.target.checked)}
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Age"
                icon={() => <AccountCircle color="primary" />}
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Job"
                icon={() => <AccountCircle color="primary" />}
              />
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </AccordionDetails>
      </Accordion>

      <FormSpacer />

      <Accordion>
        <AccordionSummary
          expandIcon={<ExpandMore />}
          aria-controls="panel1a-content"
          id="panel1a-header"
        >
          <Typography>Contact</Typography>
        </AccordionSummary>
        <AccordionDetails>
          <Grid container spacing={3}>
            <Grid container item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Address"
                icon={() => <HomeRounded color="primary" />}
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid container item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Email"
                icon={() => <AccountCircle color="primary" />}
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid container item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Phone"
                icon={() => <PhoneAndroidRounded color="primary" />}
              />
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </AccordionDetails>
      </Accordion>

      <Accordion>
        <AccordionSummary
          expandIcon={<ExpandMore />}
          aria-controls="panel1a-content"
          id="panel1a-header"
        >
          <Typography>Media</Typography>
        </AccordionSummary>
        <AccordionDetails>
          <Grid container spacing={3}>
            <Grid container item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Address"
                icon={() => <HomeRounded color="primary" />}
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid container item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Email"
                icon={() => <AccountCircle color="primary" />}
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid container item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Phone"
                icon={() => <PhoneAndroidRounded color="primary" />}
              />
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </AccordionDetails>
      </Accordion> */}
    </form>
  );
}

export default ProfileForm;
